page.title: 10MARCHWIEL CARNIVAL
page.content: THIS YEAR THE MARCHWIEL CARNIVAL WAS ON 16TH JUNE.PEOPLE ARE UP AT 7.00 AM TO PUT THE REFRESHMENT TENT UP.MORE PEOPLE COME EVERY YEAR BECAUSE OF THE FIVE ASIDE OR THE BAND OR JUST FOR A DAY OUT.THE FIVE ASIDE IS A BIG THING, IT IS HELD A WEEK BEFORE THE CARNVAL AND MANY TEAMS COME TO GET A PLACE THE NEXT SATURDAY.THE CARNIVAL STARTS AT 12.00 O,CLOCK AT THE YORKE CLOSE AND WALKS ALL THE WAY AROUND THE VILLAGE.BY 12.00 THE TENTS ARE ALL UP AND PEOPLE ARE GOING IN.THE MAIN GROUND ON THE FIELD IS THE FIVE ASIDE PITCH WHERE CHILDRENS RACES ARE GOING ON.LAST YEAR THERE WAS A PRAM RACE BUT THIS YEAR WE DID NOT HAVE ENOUGH TIME TO SET IT UP.THERE IS A DRESSING UP COMPETITION WHERE EVERY PERSON HAS TO WALK AROUND THE PITCH.THE CARNIVAL STARTED BEFORE I WAS BORN.
